settings.description: just like how the real e-reader levels have a two part special that's all about one tough as nails challenge.. instead of an airship, you get a huge castle! watch out, The Big Boo awaits you!
Ya know, while fire snakes are meant to be reddish orange... they look really good with a cool blue, so... why not build a nice chilly sky level featuring them for one?~

Fly, slide and spin through the sky and Bowser's castle!
(For Smaghetti Build Contest #2.)

Goomba's shoes? Venus flytraps spewing up spiky balls? Nipper plants breathing fire? What is this, some sort of Mario game? 

Prod. Code - 103A/104A/106A - 6/22/22, Wed-11:45 am
Pulley Platforms react to the Mario Bros.'s weight. Always keep an eye on both platforms at the same time and make sure you have the room you need to jump!
This is piranha plant on the sky😶‍🌫

so much sand, with so many coins found deep under such! think you can unearth enough for a nice three extra lives?
don't forget to check what's in the bricks as well!

Super Mario Advance 4 but it's a coin hunt.
Find all the 3 Ace-Coins and the 1 E-Coin

who would've thought that such a strange combo would come to be! best to learn how to use them though, and swim swiftly about with such!
PS: I am bad at underwater levels.
